
Topics:
  table(design table task)
  Table: row & columns
  thead -> table heading
  tr -> table row
  th -> cell heading
  td -> cell data, align attr, colspan

  basic styling, CSS ---> Cascading Style Sheet --> beautification, cosmetic of webpage
    styling possible only under certain keys with certain values
      key: value ( set keys already defined for css with certains values )
    property & value eg: color: red; --> color -> prop red -> value

  forms:
    input element, label
    form submit
  
  ways to use css
    inline
      using CSS inside style attribute is called inline styling

    internal
      using CSS style tag is called internal styling

    external
      using css in external in external css file and linking it with link tag

  
  Priority:
    Default Priority:
      inline > line of execution ( internal or enternal ( which get executed the last takes over the priority ) ) of styles

    Overwrite the Default:
      use of important ---> overrride the default priority order.
  
